  "description": {
    "zh": "我这还缺两把枪，都是北约武器。一把 G36，一把 TX-15 DML。你愿意再出把力吗？\n\n太好了！G36 要求弹容量不少于 40 发，同时还得能折叠。TX-15 要求更高，需要非常高的人体工学，还要能支持 1500 米射程，而且整体不能太大。具体要求我都列出来了。\n\nG36 要求：\n - 后坐力总和小于 250\n - 重量小于 4.4 公斤\n - 人机功效 55 或更高\n - 耐久度至少 90 %\n - 弹匣容量 40 或更多\n - 把枪托折叠起来\n - 射击距离 800米 或更多\n - 必须安装HK G36照门\n - 任意 必须安装HK G36准星\n\nTX-15 要求：\n - 后坐力总和小于 280\n - 重量小于 3.7 公斤\n - 人机功效 95 或更高\n - 耐久度至少 90 %\n - 弹匣容量 30 或更多\n - 宽度占用 5格 或更少 同时 高度占用 2格 或更少\n - 射击距离超过1500",
    "en": "I need two more guns for my guys, western guns. A G36 and a TX-15 DML, can you help out again?\n\nGreat! Alright so the G36 needs to hold at least fourty rounds in the magazine and still needs to be foldable. The TX-15 needs to be very ergonomic and capable of taking a shot from over fifteen-hundred meters away, also needs to be compact. You'll have all the further specifications written down again as always.\n\nG36 Requirements :\n - Recoil Sum less than 250\n - Weight less than 4.4 KG\n - Ergonomics 55 or higher\n - Durability higher than 90 %\n - Magazine Capacity of 40 or more\n - Sighting Range of 800 Meters or more\n - HK G36 rear sight\n - HK G36 Front Sight\n\nTX-15 Requirements :\n - Recoil Sum less than 280\n - Weight less than 3.7 KG\n - Ergonomics 95 or higher\n - Durability higher than 90 %\n - Magazine Capacity of 30 or more\n - Width of 5 slots or less and Height of 2 slots or less\n - Sighting Range of 1500 Meters or more"
  },
